        "created_at": "2018-04-20T16:37:25.639Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It would be helpful in the change log to indicate when the software went private.  This would help those of us who had built software around FDB to understand what changes were made after we shelved our work and it will make it easier to get up to speed if we decide to resurrect our work (something I am eager to do).</p>",
